Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103166,104500}A little to the right. Lower…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111883,113843}Saint Paulia School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113926,116679}St. Paulia Academy's festival\Nis almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:01.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117472,121684}Our school has a little ritual\Nthat has become a tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:10.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125855,130777}Tada! Feast your eyes.\NThis is Mikami's locker key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130943,133363}Really? The real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134322,135823}I'm gonna hang it up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136032,138701}Meimi, what's this about a lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140912,142163}It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142330,145291}Honestly Seira, you're so dense\Nwhen it comes to things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146250,149879}Okay? If there's a boy you like,\Nyou get hold of his lock…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:32.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150338,152757}then attach it to the fence\Non the east side of the roof…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:37.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153007,157345}then, at the festival's finale,\Nthat boy will ask you to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158930,161474}So that's why that fence\Nis covered with locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161766,166604}That's right. It proves that you have\Nhis feelings locked to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:52.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168690,172443}The big problem is how to get\Nthe lock there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:56.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173319,176781}Ryoko, please, please\Nask Yamamoto for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176989,178950}What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179283,181452}Hey, I've got the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:09.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186040,189961}I wonder if he's\Nalready given his lock to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193673,195800}Asuka, put your leg in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196050,197802}What for? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198094,199595}Heave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199762,201723}Hey! Hey! What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204350,207061}Junior in a bag, ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:30.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207353,210440}Do you think doing this kind\Nof thing to someone is funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212150,213484}I guess I have\Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216863,220032}The Scoop Picture Causes\NTrouble at the School Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231711,233796}Is anything troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234547,236424}You can tell me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242680,246309}Miss Mimori… I mean, sister,\Nhave you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247101,250062}About how to get a partner\Nfor the festival's dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250772,252774}Oh that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253649,255693}Lucky, I just heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:23.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256402,263242}A friend of mine asked me\Nto get this boy's lock for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:30.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264118,270541}But when I went to talk to him, Sawatari\Nfrom the school paper took our picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284138,285056}Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285264,287767}Yeah, that shot was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289560,291062}Sawatari, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294398,296359}What are you going\Nto do with that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296818,300238}Put it in the school paper, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:06.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301364,306786}I'll call it 'The Trading of Love Tokens'.\NHow's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307662,311040}You can't do that.\NI was only doing a favor for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:15.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311707,315670}That won't show on the picture,\Nso it's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317088,318005}You can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322552,325429}The problem is,\NI already have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:29.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326806,329976}If that picture is published,\Nit'll cause a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334772,336065}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:41.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337233,341153}Sawatari is that guy who will\Ndo anything for a story, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:47.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344448,347159}He's also quite popular\Nwith the girls in the school…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:51.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347493,351831}Yes, I know. I hope there's some way\Nwe can get that film from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352832,354500}Alright, I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:58.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354959,358170}St. Tail will teach that enemy\Nof girls a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359797,363342}The big problem is,\Nwe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:08.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363801,368014}Can you send your challenge out\Nbefore he develops the pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:09.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368431,369390}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369432,371183}But when will be a\Ngood time to do the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371350,372727}Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:17.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372935,377064}The Festival is the day after tomorrow.\NAll the students will be staying late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:21.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377899,381235}Everyone's free to wear\Na costume during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381485,383446}That should be the perfect day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:25.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384238,385156}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:31.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385990,391704}It wouldn't look suspicious to see\None or two people dressed as St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393372,394707}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397001,398127}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399420,401380}A St. Tail costume?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401964,404592}That's right! See!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:49.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405009,409847}We made it for you because, being so\Nathletic, you're perfect for the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410056,411223}Now wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:53.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411307,413726}Let's rehearse for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413809,415436}You're right. Let's dress her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:57.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415603,417605}And your hair has\Ngot to be in a ponytail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417730,418856}Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418940,420441}Relax, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420733,422652}This is just plain silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423569,424362}Don't fidget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424904,426739}You girls! You have got to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427239,430034}You're ruining the image of St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430576,432119}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434789,436040}What exactly did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436123,438000}Exactly what it sounded like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438334,439835}How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444215,447134}And I thought I'd\Nget a cute shot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447259,450596}But I think that big piece of junk\Ngot in the picture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451973,454141}Don't refer to me as a piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455101,456519}It's Sawatari, now is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456686,460481}Oh well.\NHere, a present for you anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465319,466153}This is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:51.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467196,471367}"I will come to the\Nschool festival to take Sawatari's film."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472118,473953}It's a challenge from St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474161,476163}Really? You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480459,483587}A big piece of junk in the way, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:08.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486090,488509}Journalism Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489176,491137}You're a real pest, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491762,494640}St. Tail says she's\Ncoming for your film…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495808,498185}I can protect my own stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:23.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498853,503733}You think I'd trust the guy\Nwho keeps letting St. Tail get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505443,507570}I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514368,517288}You're always trying to be\Nthe center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517538,519540}You're beneath my concern, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527757,530384}For the time being,\NI've got to hide the film someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:53.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530885,533179}I guess the locker\Nshould be okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538309,540144}Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543105,545524}Hey, what are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546400,548611}We'd like to have your lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:13.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549070,553282}Gee, sorry, but I only have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:16.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553699,556869}That's okay! We bought you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:17.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557244,557828}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557995,559205}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559497,561373}Put these on his locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561791,563542}Just a moment, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564835,567171}your new locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:30.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568964,570674}Sawatari\NWhat is this…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572218,574386}And don't you dare take them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576555,578182}I don't think I have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578390,579934}We'll come take them off later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584146,586482}They shouldn't make\Nso many of these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588317,591654}Darn! This is stupid! Where am\NI gonna hide this film?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597576,599203}Asuka
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:02.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599870,602540}Boy, Asuka sure is careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:04.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603749,604750}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604875,607419}Maybe I'll stash the film in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608045,610923}I doubt any of the\Ngirls would want his lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611632,613592}It's probably safer in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614176,615719}What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616554,618430}Isn't that Asuka's locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620224,622226}I… well… it's not…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626480,629525}Why did you do that?!\NNow it's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629650,632736}Why did you do that?!\NNow I can't get Junior's lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:33.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632862,633737}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633946,636740}Darn. And I wanted\Nto dance with Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636991,638159}You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638450,639952}What did you put in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642496,645541}Oh, just something\NI didn't want to get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646000,648127}What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:52.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648961,652631}Wow. I let a girl catch me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654633,657052}I'm sure he was after\Nanother of his silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657303,659430}Aha. So the film's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660139,661724}in my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666061,668898}What are you going to do\Nwith the lock, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670649,672568}Oh, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:15.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673027,675362}So, will you let me remove your lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675529,677031}What? Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:20.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678407,680492}Oh, no!\NYou're going to give it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:24.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682369,684246}On second thought, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684955,686916}Hey, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687499,689251}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691170,693047}I kinda forgot the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695007,696884}Huh? Where'd they go?
Comment: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:37.76,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:697760,697760}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:43.76,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:703766,703766}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:48.77,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:708771,708771}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:57.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712191,717154}Saint Paulia School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736966,739468}The preparations took forever,\Nbut once it got started…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:20.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739468,740970}time passed so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741011,743555}It sure did. It's almost getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744139,745432}Where's Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746058,748060}Now that you mention it, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748185,750187}She's goofing off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752481,755859}Lord forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761198,762116}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:45.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764576,765536}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767830,769039}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785389,789268}May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789768,792938}It's getting dark. Isn't it almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793731,795774}They said it's the real St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795941,797276}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802740,805951}Eek! It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807286,808412}Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810998,811832}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813709,816795}I'm not letting you get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821800,823635}So, there you are, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824345,825846}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828849,831643}We're the St. Tail trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832644,835981}St. Tail's in the 2-A classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836231,837107}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840486,843364}She had a lot of nerve,\Nappearing in MY class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849912,852331}Eek! St. Tail's\Nin the audiovisual room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853082,854333}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854416,855667}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856085,858545}St. Tail's in the connecting walkway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858712,859880}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860631,861882}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862925,865010}Darn you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866136,867721}Is this where you are, Saint Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868806,871767}Hurry up and Join!\NOne Million Saint Tails Planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872393,874478}Yes it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876855,877815}Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878315,881402}Stop dressing everyone\Nup like St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:43.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881944,883946}Spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884029,885823}Every girl in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:48.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885989,888033}Hey, isn't that St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:48.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888575,888909}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889118,891078}Where's St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907469,909471}Our decoy operation was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909763,911265}Everyone's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924945,926613}The film's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927698,930451}The festival's finale will soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930826,932703}The festival's finale will soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932870,934163}All those interested in\Nparticipating please change…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934288,936290}and assemble on the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936415,938167}I want this lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:42.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938375,942546}Sure, it's just a silly superstition,\Nbut what if it does come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942754,943714}Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944465,945966}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946675,949303}You thought everyone was out\Non the grounds, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949803,951430}But you couldn't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:53.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951930,953140}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:54.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953307,954808}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:58.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955309,958187}And don't forget me,\Nhand over the film, you little thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965777,968614}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977915,978665}What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:23.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981001,983670}Geez! Asuka, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985088,987341}You're playing dirty, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992179,995098}Would you mind… if I took this lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:37.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996308,997142}What the heck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:41.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997226,1001021}Take it for all I care, just\Ncome out and fight fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002648,1003815}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018664,1021416}Let's see, the east side is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029925,1031009}Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031510,1032594}St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034054,1035556}Now you'll get yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036223,1037599}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:18.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037933,1038809}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:20.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039393,1040477}Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048110,1050237}It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:31.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050571,1051697}You're kidding, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054116,1055033}I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055450,1057744}There's nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057869,1059496}Give me back my film!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069881,1072050}Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072259,1074219}Please forgive this commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078265,1079474}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.60,0:18:00.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079600,1080601}A balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081310,1083103}Someone's floating up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083228,1084813}And in a bag, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085397,1086982}It's Junior-in-a-bag. And…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087232,1088650}Sawatari-in-a-bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093322,1094823}You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095032,1097576}Don't just stand there like dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097659,1099870}St. Tail, put us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100037,1102789}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104499,1106543}St. Tail disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112924,1115719}Junior and Sawatari have also…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116053,1117054}disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124978,1126438}I return this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126438,1127439}Oh, the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129483,1130651}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134029,1135072}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137199,1138992}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142579,1143664}Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143914,1145374}How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147042,1148585}Uh, she did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:11.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151046,1151963}Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153507,1154216}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154633,1155467}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:19.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155550,1159054}Will you dance with me?\NIt's no fun dancing by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159221,1161306}I… um… no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161640,1163642}But why not? Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163892,1165477}But, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166269,1169690}What'll I do?\NI was going to ask Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169773,1170232}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173110,1174069}I said hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:38.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177781,1178323}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181326,1183286}Hey! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:48.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183829,1188375}I… but… it hurts,\Nyou don't have to pull so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189292,1190669}You'd better explain that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191837,1194089}You're always whacking\Nme with a broom…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194256,1196508}so why couldn't you tell\Nhim to back off there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197259,1200011}If you didn't want to go,\Nyou should have made it clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200637,1201930}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213817,1217446}Oh, you don't hate me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:20.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219406,1220365}The charm…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232878,1234337}it actually worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241178,1247434}Rats! Darn that St. Tail!\NI'll make you pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249728,1251188}Ouch!
